{"tid":1970081,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】美眾議院批譚德塞言論無根據    台口罩運抵美國","createTime":"2020-04-13T01:25:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T01:36:52.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"86a1d36f8c57ffa9c0fb88a0c9c9a0716e6378f0","tid":1970081,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T01:25:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/UR9NOH2X4CS_7zYV1CwqKw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-04/71b3e870-7c82-11ea-abb7-0c8c2d1e70f3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FUR9NOH2X4CS_7zYV1CwqKw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-04%2F71b3e870-7c82-11ea-abb7-0c8c2d1e70f3&h=98f87c91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n世界衞生組織（WHO）譚德塞近日指控台灣對其發表種族歧視言論，台當局隨即表示抗議並要求他道歉。美國眾議院外交委員會主席恩格爾上周六（11日）在社交網Twitter表示，譚德塞對台灣指控毫無依據。<br />\n<br />\n對於譚德塞的指控，台灣的蔡英文總統早前在Twitter回應稱，台方反對任何形式的歧視，又希望藉機會邀請譚德塞訪台，了解當地的防疫努力。恩格爾轉發蔡英文的Twitter，又贊成譚德塞應到台灣看看，認為這樣才能推動世衞組織的全球衞生工作。<br />\n<br />\n美國前駐聯合國大使黑利同日也發Twitter表示，美國人有權知道世衞為何忽略台灣，只聽從中國，認為世衞有需要回應這問題。<br />\n<br />\n此外，台灣早前宣布捐贈1000萬個醫用口罩給予受新冠疫情影響嚴重的國家，其中200萬個近日已運抵美國，分別由駐美各地台灣辦事處代轉給當地政府。當地上周五（10日），10萬個口罩運抵科羅拉多州丹佛市，並由駐丹佛台北經濟文化辦事處處長張詩瑞親自贈給當地政府。"},{"pid":"764b1fd94fb6d2d367e5395b57af7c06f6b9bb10","tid":1970081,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T01:34:50.000Z","msg":"侵的國策師大罵痰書記手上沾满世界人民血<br />\n<br />\n針對中共喉舌《環球時報》對美國和台灣的不實指責，#班農 戲虐嘲諷稱  「《環球時報》根本不配做中共大外宣」，「應該集體被解雇，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">他們讓習近平看起來像個白痴」</span></span>，「一群三流水平的貨色」。 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">貪得塞、中共，你們的手上沾滿了世界人民的鮮血！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/globalhimalaya/status/1249457413335314433?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fglobalhimalaya%2Fstatus%2F1249457413335314433%3Fs%3D21&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWQ8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=ac561841\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fglobalhimalaya%2Fstatus%2F1249457413335314433%3Fs%3D21&h=d6672d1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/globalhimalaya/status/1249457413335314433?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n罵得精彩，罵得熱血沸騰！"},{"pid":"87356c753c524030971eb830dfafdd0b83d61a52","tid":1970081,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T01:36:52.000Z","msg":"補<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/GlobalHimalaya/status/1249457413335314433\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGlobalHimalaya%2Fstatus%2F1249457413335314433&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWQ8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=6598594a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGlobalHimalaya%2Fstatus%2F1249457413335314433&h=2b02a1ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/GlobalHimalaya/status/1249457413335314433</a>"}]}